.TH "mipi_dsi_dcs_read" 9 "mipi_dsi_dcs_read" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
mipi_dsi_dcs_read \- send DCS read request command
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "ssize_t" mipi_dsi_dcs_read
.BI "(struct mipi_dsi_device *dsi "  ","
.BI "u8 cmd "  ","
.BI "void *data "  ","
.BI "size_t len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dsi" 12
DSI peripheral device
.IP "cmd" 12
DCS command
.IP "data" 12
buffer in which to receive data
.IP "len" 12
size of receive buffer
.SH "RETURN"
The number of bytes read or a negative error code on failure.
